OL,7,FA lorry driving instructor from North
OL,8,FWales has reflected on the 'problems'
OL,9,Fcaused by the new 20mph limits, a
OL,10,Fweek after it was implemented across
OL,11,FWales.
OL,13,FAs of September 17, 30mph roads have
OL,14,Fbeen reduced to 20mph where cars mix
OL,15,Fwith pedestrians and cyclists.
OL,17,FLast week, lorry driving instructor
OL,18,FStuart Walker spoke to ITV News Wales
OL,19,Fabout the new law. He said the
OL,20,Fchanges are going to cause gridlock
OL,21,Fat rush hour.
OL,3,C20mph a week on: 'It's created more
OL,4,Cproblems than it's solved', says
OL,5,Clorry driving instructor
